Thanks for the feedback! If your issue is related to the Flutter framework itself,
please open an issue at
[github.com/flutter/flutter](https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/new).

## Steps to Reproduce

1. open project in android studio
1. move/refactor some dart files under `lib` from a directory to another directory, both directory are under `lib`.
2. move expection dialog shown `Exception when attempting to compute the file changes for the file move: Server error: The `edit.getRefactoring` request was cancelled."`
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2276718/87511742-6cc6e180-c6a8-11ea-944d-b302bc1ef172.png)
3. The dart files moved, but the imports are not changed, so the code broken.


_Please tell us what you were doing and what went wrong_
